Package org.wfp.fittest.config

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AppConfig
    Global application config.
    PersistenceConfig
    PersistenceConfig defines the configuration options for the data source used FITTESTPlanner.
    RestConfig
    Configures the REST servlet.
    ServletConfig
    Configures the behavior for the JSP servlet.
    WebConfig
    Configures spring data web and exports resource handlers.
    WebInitializer
    WebInitializer is an annotated configuration class which replaces the web.xml file used in XML based configurations.
